# Web Client SPA Routes
# Explicitly match specific Web Client routes to ensure they hit the Web Client index
/form/*  /index.html  200
/        /index.html  200

# Flutter SPA Routes (Explicit)
# Redirect specific Flutter routes to the renamed Flutter entry point
/login   /flutter.html  200
/admin   /flutter.html  200
/transfer /flutter.html 200

# Fallback (Flutter)
# Any other route not matched above falls back to Flutter
/*       /flutter.html  200
